---
title: Rosemary and Butter-Basted Steak with Roasted Parsnip and Garlicky Creamed Spinach
description: Get ready to learn a trick that steakhouses don’t want you to know about—butter-basting! Finishing steak with an herb and garlic-infused butter is how they take meat to the next level.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rosemary-basted-steak-a65f86ca.jpg
